00:00:14.245 --> 00:00:18.385
She is orphan. She has never known her father and lost her mother when she was two.

00:00:18.585 --> 00:00:23.423
Her adoptive family lives in poor conditions in a shack with no bathroom.

00:00:24.157 --> 00:00:27.261
Often, her meal is a handful of corn only.

00:00:28.095 --> 00:00:30.697
In January 2010, everything got worse.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:36.403
An earthquake killed more than two hundred thousand people and one million and a half has turned homeless.

00:00:36.570 --> 00:00:41.642
The country, which is very poor, has found itself with fewer resources available to help the people.

00:00:42.009 --> 00:00:48.916
